  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Customer Engagement Rep",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Customer Engagement Representative</strong></h2><p>At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, we work directly with brands to create strong, face-to-face customer experiences through events, roadshows, and outreach campaigns.<br />This role is suited for individuals who enjoy working with people, learning on the ground, and developing practical communication and sales skills in a team-based environment.</p><h3><strong>Role Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Engage customers through professional, face-to-face interactions</p></li><li><p>Represent client brands at events, roadshows, and outreach activities</p></li><li><p>Communicate brand messages clearly and confidently</p></li><li><p>Work closely with team members to support campaigns and deliver positive customer experiences</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Provide</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Full training provided (no prior experience required)</p></li><li><p>Performance-based growth with clear development pathways</p></li><li><p>Exposure to different campaigns and working locations</p></li><li><p>Supportive mentorship, coaching, and team guidance</p></li></ul><h3><strong>This Role Is Suitable For Individuals Who</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Are comfortable interacting with people or are keen to develop this skill</p></li><li><p>Are reliable, motivated, and open to learning</p></li><li><p>Enjoy active, on-the-ground work environments</p></li><li><p>Are able to commit to a full-time role</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you are interested in gaining hands-on experience in customer engagement and brand representation, we would be happy to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
